comments: Bilello is cool & has an interesting subject matter but honestly i felt intimidated asking questions, not because of him but because of all the jocks in my class, which i hear isn\'t uncommon for Bilello\'s classes. Tests are easy if you study the guide he gives you. Also gives you the chance to work a Lacrosse event for A grade on a paper, do it!
Andy\'s an awesome teacher. He knows his stuff. I highly recommend taking him.
